FTC Information¶

ftc¶

Get information on an FTC team from FTC-Events. If no subcommand is specified, the team subcommand is inferred, and the argument is taken as a team number.

`{prefix}ftc 5667` - show information on team 5667, Robominers

team¶

Get information on an FTC team by number.

`{prefix}ftc team 7244` - show information on team 7244, OUT of the BOX Robotics
